    {
      "id": "6576b5f87515",
      "name": "Roadmap Autonomy Engine \u2014 Overnight (1am-7am Sydney)",
      "prompt": "Run the Roadmap Autonomy Engine for Sean \u2014 the next-generation overnight engine.\n\nExecute:\n```\ncd /opt/data/hermes-sync && python3 scripts/roadmap_engine.py --phase all\n```\n\nPhase 1 (Research): Clone/pull tracked repos, scan TODOs/FIXMEs, fetch GitHub issues, revise roadmap.json, snapshot to roadmap-history/\nPhase 2 (Execute): Execute pending tasks (test/code/research/browser/review types) until 14:00 UTC (midnight Sydney)\nPhase 3 (Report): Generate narrative report to workspace/plans/nightly-reports/report-YYYY-MM-DD.md, deliver critical issues to Telegram\n\nRoadmap lives at: workspace/plans/roadmap.json\nKey projects: ChonSong/repo-transmute, ChonSong/everything-dashboard, ChonSong/hermes-sync, NousResearch/hermes-agent",
