      "name": "CI failure notifier",
      "prompt": "Check CI status for ChonSong/agent-os and report any failures from the most recent run.\n\nGitHub token: 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\n\nSteps:\n1. GET https://api.github.com/repos/ChonSong/agent-os/actions/runs?per_page=3\n2. Check if the most recent run has conclusion \"failure\"\n3. If there are failures, report which workflow failed and what the last successful commit SHA was\n4. If all recent runs are successful, report \"All CI green\"\n\nDo NOT try to fix anything \u2014 just report. Save any failure info to /opt/data/hermes-sync/projects/agent-os/logs/ci-status.log\n",
