    {
      "id": "4706cc1362bb",
      "name": "agent-os: Kickoff \u2014 pre-flight",
      "prompt": "## agent-os: Kickoff Pre-Flight Check\n\nVerify repo state before the build phases begin.\n\n### Context\n\nAll git/gh operations must be done via SSH to the host:\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"cd /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os && git pull origin main 2>&1\"\n```\n\nGitHub operations use the host's gh CLI (already authenticated via keyring \u2014 no token needed).\n\nThe agent-os repo is at `/home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/` on the host.\n\n### Steps\n\n1. Check CI status:\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"gh run list --repo ChonSong/agent-os --limit 3 2>&1\"\n```\n\n2. Check what's in deploy.yml:\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"cat /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/.github/workflows/deploy.yml 2>&1\"\n```\n\n3. Check if Dockerfile exists:\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"ls /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/Dockerfile 2>&1 || echo 'No Dockerfile'\"\n```\n\n4. Check Go stubs:\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"cat /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/infra/CasaOS/agent/go.mod\"\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"cat /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/infra/CasaOS/webhook-emitter/go.mod\"\n```\n\n5. Check dashboard backend entry point:\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"ls /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/apps/dashboard/backend/src/ 2>&1\"\n```\n\n6. Check current git state:\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"cd /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os && git log --oneline -3 && git status --short\"\n```\n\n### Deliver\n\nReport:\n1. CI status (pass/fail for recent runs)\n2. Confirm deploy.yml is the TODO stub\n3. Any Dockerfile exists?\n4. Go modules state\n5. Dashboard backend state\n6. Any red flags for Phase 1\n",
      "skills": [],
      "skill": null,
      "model": null,
      "provider": null,
      "base_url": null,
      "script": null,
      "context_from": null,
      "schedule": {
