    {
      "id": "78c7c5433ddc",
      "name": "agent-os: Phase 1 \u2014 Deploy pipeline",
      "prompt": "## agent-os Phase 1 \u2014 Deploy Pipeline Fix\n\n**Goal**: Fix the broken CI \"Build and Push Agent OS\" workflow.\n\n**IMPORTANT**: All git operations via SSH to host. No GitHub tokens in prompts. gh CLI on host is already authenticated.\n\n### Pattern for all gh/git commands:\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"cd /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os && YOUR_COMMAND_HERE\"\n```\n\n### Steps\n\n**Step 1 \u2014 Create files on host**\n\nSSH to host and create these files:\n\na) `/tmp/agent-os/docker-bake.hcl`:\n```\nvariable \"IMAGE_TAG\" {\n  default = \"latest\"\n}\n\nvariable \"GITHUB_SHA\" {\n  default = \"local\"\n}\n\ngroup \"default\" {\n  targets = [\"agent-os\"]\n}\n\ntarget \"agent-os\" {\n  context    = \"./\"\n  dockerfile = \"Dockerfile\"\n  platforms  = [\"linux/amd64\", \"linux/arm64\"]\n  tags = [\n    \"ghcr.io/chonsong/agent-os:${IMAGE_TAG}\",\n    \"ghcr.io/chonsong/agent-os:${GITHUB_SHA}\"\n  ]\n  cache-from = [\"ghcr.io/chonsong/agent-os:buildcache\"]\n  cache-to   = [\"type=registry,ref=ghcr.io/chonsong/agent-os:buildcache,mode=max\"]\n  pull       = true\n  args = {\n    BUILDKIT_INLINE_CACHE = \"1\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nb) `Dockerfile` in the agent-os repo root. The Dockerfile should build all three components:\n```dockerfile\n# syntax=docker/dockerfile:1\n\n# \u2500\u2500 Stage 1: Frontend \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nFROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-build\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY package*.json ./\nRUN npm ci\nCOPY src ./src\nRUN npm run build\n\n# \u2500\u2500 Stage 2: Backend \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nFROM node:20-alpine AS backend-build\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY package*.json ./\nRUN npm ci\nCOPY src ./src\nRUN npm run build\n\n# \u2500\u2500 Stage 3: Nanobot \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nFROM python:3.12-slim AS nanobot-build\nRUN pip install --no-cache-dir nanobot-ai[api]\nWORKDIR /workspace\n\n# \u2500\u2500 Stage 4: Runtime \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nFROM python:3.12-slim\nENV PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1\nWORKDIR /app\n\n# Install nanobot\nRUN pip install --no-cache-dir nanobot-ai[api] httpx\n\n# Copy nanobot workspace scaffold\nWORKDIR /workspace\nRUN mkdir -p /workspace && echo '{\"agents\": []}' > /workspace/agents.json\n\n# Copy dashboard backend\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY --from=backend-build /app/dist ./dist\nCOPY --from=backend-build /app/package*.json ./\nRUN npm ci --omit=dev\n\n# Copy frontend build\nCOPY --from=frontend-build /app/dist ./public\n\n# Expose ports\nEXPOSE 3001 8900\n\n# Entry point\nCMD [\"sh\", \"-c\", \"pip install nanobot-ai[api] -q && nanobot serve --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8900 & node /app/dist/index.js\"]\n```\n\nc) `docker-compose.prod.yml`:\n```yaml\nversion: \"3.9\"\n\nservices:\n  agent-os:\n    image: ghcr.io/chonsong/agent-os:latest\n    restart: unless-stopped\n    ports:\n      - \"3001:3001\"   # dashboard backend\n      - \"8900:8900\"   # nanobot\n    environment:\n      MINIMAX_API_KEY: ${MINIMAX_API_KEY}\n      NANOBOT_WORKSPACE: /workspace\n    volumes:\n      - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock:ro\n```\n\n**Step 2 \u2014 Fix deploy.yml**\n\nSSH to host and write this to `/home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/.github/workflows/deploy.yml`:\n```yaml\nname: Deploy\n\non:\n  release:\n    types: [published]\n  workflow_dispatch:\n    inputs:\n      image_tag:\n        required: false\n        default: 'latest'\n\njobs:\n  build-and-push:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    permissions:\n      contents: read\n      packages: write\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - name: Set up QEMU\n        uses: docker/setup-qemu-action@v3\n\n      - name: Set up Docker Buildx\n        uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\n\n      - name: Login to GitHub Container Registry\n        uses: docker/login-action@v3\n        with:\n          registry: ghcr.io\n          username: ${{ github.actor }}\n          password: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n\n      - name: Bake from file\n        uses: docker/bake-action@v4\n        with:\n          file: docker-bake.hcl\n          set: |\n            IMAGE_TAG=${{ github.event.inputs.image_tag || 'latest' }}\n            GITHUB_SHA=${{ github.sha }}\n          push: true\n          pull: true\n```\n\n**Step 3 \u2014 Commit and push**\n\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"cd /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os && git add docker-bake.hcl Dockerfile docker-compose.prod.yml .github/workflows/deploy.yml && git commit -m 'feat: implement deploy pipeline (docker-bake.hcl, Dockerfile, docker-compose.prod)' && git push origin main\"\n```\n\n**Step 4 \u2014 Verify CI**\n\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"gh run list --repo ChonSong/agent-os --limit 3\"\n```\n\nWait ~60s and check again if a new run appeared. If it fails, look at logs and fix in a follow-up commit.\n\n### Deliver\n\nReport:\n1. Files created (list them)\n2. Git commit sha\n3. CI status after push (pass/fail + run id)\n4. Any errors requiring manual intervention\n",
