      "id": "b458ca116bdb",
      "name": "agent-os: Phase 5 \u2014 Cloudflare TF",
      "prompt": "## agent-os Phase 5 \u2014 Cloudflare Terraform Infrastructure\n\n**Goal**: Create Terraform infrastructure for Cloudflare tunnel + Access policy.\n\n**IMPORTANT**: All git/gh via SSH to host. Pattern:\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"cd /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os && YOUR_COMMAND\"\n```\n\n### Steps\n\n**Step 1 \u2014 Create Terraform directory and files**\n\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"mkdir -p /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/infra/terraform\"\n```\n\nCreate `/home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/infra/terraform/main.tf`:\n```hcl\nterraform {\n  required_version = \">= 1.6\"\n  required_providers {\n    cloudflare = {\n      source  = \"cloudflare/cloudflare\"\n      version = \"~> 4\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nprovider \"cloudflare\" {\n  api_token = var.cloudflare_api_token\n}\n\nvariable \"cloudflare_api_token\" {\n  description = \"Cloudflare API token (set via TF_VAR_cloudflare_api_token env var)\"\n  type        = string\n  sensitive   = true\n}\n\nvariable \"cloudflare_account_id\" {\n  description = \"Cloudflare account ID\"\n  type        = string\n}\n\nvariable \"zone_id\" {\n  description = \"Cloudflare zone ID for codeovertcp.com\"\n  type        = string\n}\n\nvariable \"domain\" {\n  description = \"Domain for the tunneled application\"\n  type        = string\n  default     = \"appexample.codeovertcp.com\"\n}\n\nvariable \"github_org\" {\n  description = \"GitHub organization for Access policy\"\n  type        = string\n  default     = \"ChonSong\"\n}\n\nvariable \"tunnel_secret\" {\n  description = \"Tunnel secret (set via TF_VAR_tunnel_secret env var)\"\n  type        = string\n  sensitive   = true\n}\n\n# \u2500\u2500 Tunnel \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nresource \"cloudflare_tunnel\" \"agent_os\" {\n  account_id = var.cloudflare_account_id\n  name       = \"agent-os-tunnel\"\n  secret     = var.tunnel_secret\n}\n\nresource \"cloudflare_tunnel_route\" \"agent_os\" {\n  zone_id   = var.zone_id\n  tunnel_id = cloudflare_tunnel.agent_os.id\n  domain    = var.domain\n}\n\n# \u2500\u2500 Access Policy \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nresource \"cloudflare_access_application\" \"agent_os\" {\n  account_id = var.cloudflare_account_id\n  name       = \"agent-os\"\n  domain     = var.domain\n}\n\nresource \"cloudflare_access_policy\" \"agent_os\" {\n  application_id = cloudflare_access_application.agent_os.id\n  name           = \"GitHub org members \u2014 ChonSong\"\n  include {\n    github {\n      organizations = [var.github_org]\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n# \u2500\u2500 Outputs \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\noutput \"tunnel_id\" {\n  value       = cloudflare_tunnel.agent_os.id\n  description = \"Tunnel UUID (use with cloudflared connect)\"\n}\n\noutput \"tunnel_name\" {\n  value       = cloudflare_tunnel.agent_os.name\n  description = \"Tunnel name\"\n}\n\noutput \"access_domain\" {\n  value = cloudflare_access_application.agent_os.domain\n}\n```\n\nCreate `/home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/infra/terraform/variables.tf`:\n```hcl\n# variables.tf \u2014 all variables declared in main.tf via var.* references\n# No additional content needed; variables are defined inline in main.tf\n```\n\nCreate `/home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/infra/terraform/.gitignore`:\n```\n.terraform/\n.terraform.lock.hcl\n*.tfstate\n*.tfstate.*\ncrash.log\noverride.tf\n*.tfvars\nsecrets.tfvars\n```\n\nCreate `/home/sean/.hermes/agent-os/infra/terraform/README.md`:\n```markdown\n# Cloudflare Infrastructure\n\n## What this creates\n\n- Cloudflare Tunnel: `agent-os-tunnel`\n- DNS A record for `appexample.codeovertcp.com`\n- Cloudflare Access Application + Policy (GitHub OAuth \u2014 ChonSong org members only)\n\n## Setup (one-time)\n\n1. Create a Cloudflare API token with these scopes:\n   - `Account: Tunnel: Edit`\n   - `Zone: DNS: Edit`\n   - `Access: Organisations: Read`, `Access: Applications: Edit`\n\n2. Generate a tunnel secret:\n   ```bash\n   # Option A: use cloudflared\n   cloudflared tunnel secret generate agent-os-tunnel\n   \n   # Option B: generate random bytes\n   openssl rand -base64 32\n   ```\n\n3. Get your Cloudflare:\n   - Account ID: from `cloudflare.com/console/<zone>/overview`\n   - Zone ID: from the same page\n\n4. Set env vars and apply:\n   ```bash\n   export TF_VAR_cloudflare_api_token=your_token\n   export TF_VAR_cloudflare_account_id=your_account_id\n   export TF_VAR_zone_id=your_zone_id\n   export TF_VAR_tunnel_secret=your_secret\n\n   terraform init\n   terraform plan\n   terraform apply\n   ```\n\n5. Configure `cloudflared` on the server:\n   ```bash\n   cloudflared service install <tunnel_id>\n   ```\n   The tunnel credentials file is at `~/.cloudflared/<tunnel_id>.json` after first run.\n\n## Tear down\n\n```bash\nterraform destroy\n```\n```\n\n**Step 2 \u2014 Commit and push**\n\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"cd /home/sean/.hermes/agent-os && git add infra/terraform/ && git commit -m 'feat(terraform): add Cloudflare tunnel + Access policy' && git push origin main\"\n```\n\n**Step 3 \u2014 Check CI**\n\n```bash\nssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no sean@localhost \"gh run list --repo ChonSong/agent-os --limit 3\"\n```\n\n### Deliver\n\nReport:\n1. Files created (list them)\n2. Git commit sha\n3. CI status\n4. Checklist of what needs to be done manually (Cloudflare token, account ID, zone ID, tunnel secret)\n5. Note: terraform apply must be run locally \u2014 not in CI (no Cloudflare credentials in GitHub)\n",
